We need a president who respects science who understands the dangers of climate change. Unless we take urgent action the results will be more catastrophic.
My head hurts after watching that debate. I don’t know if we need another.  Especially because Trump doesn’t know how to follow the rules. He thinks he’s above the law and rules.
Biden wraps presidential debate acting presidential saying he would accept the election results. What does Trump do?  Interrupt. Because Trump doesn’t know how to do the same be presidential.
I don’t want 4 more years of these lies.  #Vote   Pass it on.
Ha. Wallace finally admits he also can’t keep up with Trump’s rantings.

Wallace going through Biden’s enviro plan and talking now about cost. No mention from Wallace about the cost of not doing it - to our planet and public health. We must act on climate change now.  And let’s be clear Trump’s plan is to bail out Big Oil with taxpayer $$

Trump knows nothing about climate change. Clearly doesn’t know what is environmental justice. He thinks our air is immaculate?  He hasn’t been to #CA44 and fails to read any air quality reports. But then remember he doesn’t read.
Omg. Biden talking about his son Beau who served in the military (and later died) and Trump interrupts to insult his other son. What a disgrace. And Wallace just allowing this bullshit.
“He’s Putin’s puppy.” -Biden. Yes he is. Trump is Putin’s puppy.
Trump has no credibility on healthcare. Remember he is trying to strip away healthcare from millions of Americans.
Can we talk about Trump breaking the law? And those in his Administration.
What the heck did Trump just say on race? I couldn’t even understand his answer on ending race sensitive training. Did i miss it or does he just have no clue what he’s talking about.
Wallace tried to scold Trump  about not interrupting and Trump pointing finger like a kid saying well he did it too.  🤦🏽‍♀️
Agree Trump is a clown. That’s putting it nicely.

Wallace asking about Biden big spending but ignores the huge deficit caused by the huge Trump tax scam? Rolling Trump tax scam back can help fund healthcare infrastructure and help the middle class. Not help billionaires get more rich.
Trump lying again. Now about his taxes. He says people who pay taxes and follow the rules are stupid.

Wallace allowing Trump to insult too. If there is a next debate can we get some decorum and rules in place that are followed. No way we could do what Trump is doing on the House floor. I get this isn’t the House floor but this is supposed to be the President.  He’s embarrassing.
Wallace allowing Trump to ramble then not giving Biden enough time to respond. And not shutting up Trump when he rudely interrupts. The mess continues.
As Biden talks to those who lost someone to COVID Trump interrupts because he has no clue how to be compassionate. And show any empathy.
Trump lying again. We are not weeks away from a vaccine.
All Trump can do is talk over Biden. Bully Trump disrespectful.
Finally Biden calls out Trump for being a liar.
